Pick up the nearest lettuce.

Chill the lettuce in the fridge and then take it out.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.

Pick the lettuce up from the table.

Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.

Put the chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward just past the fridge, turn left, move forward to alongside the fridge, turn right and move forward to the table.

Turn left, move to the counter, turn left, move to alongside the sink, turn right.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
